abstract: Javier Fernandez becomes first Spanish men's champion at figure skating world championships in Shanghai; other figure skating news noted.
lead_paragraph: Javier Fernandez cleanly landed two quad jumps in his free skate at the figure skating world championships in Shanghai on Saturday.

headline.main: For First Time, a Spaniard Figure Skater Is the World Champion
